sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Process
    participant M as Memory
    participant S as Scheduler
    P->>M: Access virtual address
    M-->>P: Page fault!
    P->>S: Block (PAGE_FAULT)
    S->>S: Context switch to next process
    M->>M: Load page from disk
    M-->>P: Page loaded
    P->>S: Unblock (READY)
